14. Governance Rules

These should be explicit from day one.

Required

* trace every artifact back to source events
* preserve user attribution
* expose credit logic in readable form
* allow audit of trust changes
* support deletion/deactivation workflows where possible

Forbidden

* hidden credit extraction
* silent repurposing of user data
* undisclosed weighting changes
* manipulation disguised as recommendation

